{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I pretended I was doing something like-- like-- like I wasn't lost in the thing, like I was do-- like I had a shovel like doing a ditch or something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anything not to look suspicious, like you know, you not-- you don't belong in here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he-- his name was Marmalade [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Franz. ?] I don't know why they called him Marmalade [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Franz. ?] But he was-- he was one of the political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- he was German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was there for a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody knew him, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- he helped me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If it wouldn't be for him I probably wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then-- and then-- and then was one incidence when I was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know-- I never-- we were working, you know, in the-- in the-- not-- you know, there was the immediate camp was the barracks, which were enclosed with barbed wire and everything.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when you were working, you were working on the outskirt of the camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they had out-- they had outposts, you know, like-- and they had with submachine guns on the outlooks and posts and things like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were working on the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was close to the German-- the German barracks and things like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I don't remember-- one time I remember-- I don't know why or something-- I was looking-- I was near the SS barracks and I was looking for some food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I got caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they got me in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I had to lay down on chairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they hit me with a stick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the stick broke.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
